    <!-- Policy Content Start -->
    <section class="policy-area pt-80 pb-80">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
            <div class="policy-content">
              <h3>1. General Policy</h3>
              <p>
                <strong>Salsa Candela operates under a no-refund policy for presale payments.</strong>
                Advance payments include significant discounts of up to 50% and guarantee your
                spot in limited-capacity classes. Instead of refunds, we offer
                flexible alternatives that adapt to our students' needs.
              </p>

              <h3>2. Group Classes (5-Week Workshops)</h3>
              <h4>2.1 No Refund Policy</h4>
              <p>
                <strong>No monetary refunds are granted</strong> for group classes paid in presale.
                The following alternatives are available:
              </p>

              <h4>2.2 Available Alternatives</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>Standby Registration:</strong> For unforeseen scheduling conflicts
                  (travel, injuries, or other commitments), your registration can be placed on standby
                  and reactivated in future course editions.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Switch to Private Classes:</strong> If you experience dissatisfaction with the
                  service (class capacity, instructor methodology, etc.), you can switch
                  your group registration for an equivalent private class package.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Transfer to Third Parties:</strong> You can transfer your registration to
                  another person with 48 hours' notice before the workshop starts.
                </li>
              </ul>

              <h3>3. Private Classes</h3>
              <h4>3.1 Private Class Package Policy</h4>
              <p>
                <strong>Private class packages are non-refundable.</strong>
                Available alternatives:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>Standby Registration:</strong> The complete package can be
                  kept on standby for future use with no expiration date.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Transfer:</strong> The package can be transferred to
                  another person at any time.
                </li>
              </ul>

              <h4>3.2 Individual Class Rescheduling</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>With 24 hours' notice:</strong> Free
                  rescheduling.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Less than 24 hours:</strong> 50% of the class value is forfeited.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>No notice:</strong> 100% of the class value is forfeited.
                </li>
              </ul>

              <h3>4. Party and Event Tickets</h3>
              <p>
                <strong>Party and event tickets are non-refundable.</strong>
                Available alternative:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>Transfer:</strong> Tickets can be transferred to another person
                  up to 24 hours before the event. After this deadline, no
                  change options are available.
                </li>
              </ul>

              <h3>5. Special Circumstances</h3>
              <h4>5.1 Cancellation by Salsa Candela</h4>
              <p>
                If Salsa Candela must cancel classes for operational,
                weather-related, or force majeure reasons:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Free rescheduling will be offered.</li>
                <li>If rescheduling is not possible, a 100% refund will be provided.</li>
              </ul>

              <h3>6. Process to Request Alternatives</h3>
              <ol>
                <li>
                  Send request via email to:
                  <strong>contacto@salsa-candela.com</strong>
                </li>
                <li>
                  Include the purchase date, access code number, and the
                  reason for the request.
                </li>
                <li>Response time: 2-5 business days.</li>
                <li>
                  Approved alternatives (standby, transfers, changes) will be
                  processed at no additional cost.
                </li>
              </ol>

              <h3>7. Transfers and Changes</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  Registrations may be transferred to other people with 48
                  hours' notice.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Schedule or branch changes subject to availability, at no
                  additional cost.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Level changes permitted during the first week of the
                  workshop.
                </li>
              </ul>

              <h3>8. Exceptions</h3>
              <p>
                <strong>This no-refund policy applies to all purchases.</strong>
                The only exception is:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Class cancellation by Salsa Candela.</li>
              </ul>

              <h3>9. Contact</h3>
              <p>
                For any questions about this policy or to process a
                refund:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> contacto@salsa-candela.com</li>
                <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +52 55 4144 3745</li>
                <li><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> +52 55 4144 3745</li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Office hours:</strong> Monday to Friday 10:00 AM -
                  6:00 PM
                </li>
              </ul>

              <div
                class="policy-footer mt-50 p-30"
                style="
                  background-color: #f8f9fa;
                  border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
                "
              >
                <p>
                  <strong>Important note:</strong> This policy is subject to
                  change. The version in effect at the time of your purchase will be the
                  one that applies to your case. <br />Last updated: September
                  2025.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
